mage-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%92%D0%B5%D1%81.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/9/91/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%92%D0%B5%D1%81.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/18?cb=20210131174204&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></span></span> 0,5 кг</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"Цена\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Стоимость</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img alt=\"Иконка Гейм Золото\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Гейм Золото.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%97%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BE.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/b/ba/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%97%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BE.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/18?cb=20210131171215&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></span></span> 25</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n</p>\n<div style=\"margin-top:1em\">\n<div style=\"display: block\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><img alt=\"Иконка Гейм Дневник\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Иконка Гейм Дневник.png\" data-image-key=\"%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%94%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/baldursgate/images/b/b3/%D0%98%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%93%D0%B5%D0%B9%D0%BC_%D0%94%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20210724193634&amp;path-prefix=ru\" /></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Kurale; font-style:italic; margin-left: 36px; margin-top: -28px; border-left: 2px ridge #4a4a4a; padding-left: 10px\">Мягкая кожаная накидка. Вышивка в виде паутины покрыта грязными пятнами, а швы, да и сама кожа, кое-где уже рассыпаются в труху.</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-style:italic; font-size:14px; padding-right:50px; color:lightcoral; text-shadow:1px 1px 2px #222, -1px 1px 2px #222, -1px -1px 2px #222, 1px -1px 2px #222; text-align:right; margin-bottom:2em\">Описание в игре</div>\n<p><b>Потрепанная накидка дроу</b> (англ. <i>Frayed Drow Hood</i>) — это <a href=\"/ru/wiki/%D0%91%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%8F_(Baldur%27s_Gate_III)/%D0%93%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B5_%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%8B\" title=\"Броня (Baldur&#39;s Gate III)/Головные уборы\">головной убор</a> в <a href=\"/ru/wiki/Baldur%27s_Gate_III\" title=\"Baldur&#39;s Gate III\">Baldur's Gate III</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\".D0.A1.D0.B2.D0.BE.D0.B9.D1.81.D1.82.D0.B2.D0.B0\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Свойства\">Свойства</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fbaldursgate.fandom.com%2Fru%2Fwiki%2F%25D0%259F%25D0%25BE%25D1%2582%25D1%2580%25D0%25B5%25D0%25BF%25D0%25B0%25D0%25BD%25D0%25BD%25D0%25B0%25D1%258F_%25D0%25BD%25D0%25B0%25D0%25BA%25D0%25B8%25D0%25B4%25D0%25BA%25D0%25B0_%25D0%25B4%25D1%2580%25D0%25BE%25D1%2583%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=ru&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:hr